<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.3">
<l>nīyumpāṅ kallaikāṇ neñcamē nīḷiravu</l>
<l>mōyum poḻutiṉṟi yūḻiyāy nīṇṭatāṟ</l>
<l>kāyuṅ kaṭuñcilaiyeṉ kākuttaṉ vārāṉāṉ</l>
<l>māyum vakaiyaṟiyēṉ valviṉaiyēṉ peṇpiṟantē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are without companion, look, heart, and long night,</l>
<l>without the time coming to an end, grows long as an aeon.</l>
<l>My Kākuttaṉ with hot fierce bow will not come.</l>
<l>I don’t know how to hide, I with harsh Karma, born as a woman.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
